## Issues Identified:
1. **JWT Token Expiration** - Tokens expiring at 11:31 AM vs current time 2:29 PM (3+ hour difference)
2. **Infinite Redirect Loop** - Usually indicates mismatched Clerk publishable/secret keys
3. **Clock Skew Detection** - System clock appears to be inaccurate

## Resolution Plan:

### Step 1: System Clock Fix
- [ ] Check current system time
- [ ] Synchronize system clock
